c: 4
v: 155
t: "Ne (khwabahelesia eshinyasio) khulwo okhufunaka khwabu indakano nende okhukhaya khwabu abimanyisio bia Nyasaye nende okhwira khwabu Abarumwa khunjila ilali yatoto, nende okhuboola khwabu mbu; “ Emioyo chiefu chekalwa, ne shichekalwa tawe, halali Nyasaye yachiupakhwo eshimanyisio khulwa obukhayi bwabu, kho shibasuubilanga halali hatiti butswa"